		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
		<title>Cursivo Site</title>
		<meta
			name="description"
			content="Public multilingual Astro marketing site for Cursivo, the AI CRM and operations layer for car rental teams."
		/>
	</head>
	<body>
		<main class="shell">
			<section class="hero">
				<p class="eyebrow">Public marketing site</p>
				<h1>Cursivo Site</h1>
				<p class="lede">
					A dedicated Astro repository for the public multilingual site for Cursivo, focused on clear
					product positioning, operational trust, and a clean implementation backlog in Linear.
				</p>
				<div class="links">
					<a href="https://github.com/RebSem/cursivo-site">GitHub repo</a>
					<a href="https://github.com/RebSem/cursivo-site/blob/main/public-marketing-site-blueprint.md">
						Technical brief
					</a>
					<a href="https://linear.app/rebsem/project/cursivo-site-48c5b90dc853">Linear project</a>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="panel">
				<h2>Initial implementation scope</h2>
				<ul>
					<li>Astro 5 foundation with deployment target deferred until the final domain is ready</li>
					<li>Warm operational visual direction carried over from the ops product</li>
					<li>Route-first multilingual architecture for English, Russian, and Arabic</li>
					<li>Implementation backlog tracked in Linear as a dedicated project</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section class="panel">
				<h2>Core questions the site must answer</h2>
				<ol>
					<li>What is Cursivo?</li>
					<li>Why is it different from a generic chatbot or CRM?</li>
					<li>Why should a rental operator trust this workflow?</li>
				</ol>
			</section>
		</main>
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	:root {
		color-scheme: light;
		--sand: #f5efe6;
		--ivory: #fffdf9;
		--ink: #142033;
		--slate: #5f6d80;
		--terracotta: #c96a3a;
		--border: rgba(113, 88, 62, 0.18);
	}

	* {
		box-sizing: border-box;
	}

	html,
	body {
		margin: 0;
		min-height: 100%;
		font-family: "Manrope", "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
		background:
			radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(201, 106, 58, 0.16), transparent 22rem),
			linear-gradient(180deg, #fff8ef 0%, var(--sand) 100%);
		color: var(--ink);
	}

	body {
		padding: 32px 20px 48px;
	}

	.shell {
		max-width: 980px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		display: grid;
		gap: 24px;
	}

	.hero,
	.panel {
		background: rgba(255, 253, 249, 0.86);
		border: 1px solid var(--border);
		border-radius: 24px;
		padding: 28px;
		box-shadow: 0 16px 48px rgba(20, 32, 51, 0.08);
	}

	.eyebrow {
		margin: 0 0 12px;
		font-family: "IBM Plex Mono", "SFMono-Regular", monospace;
		font-size: 0.78rem;
		letter-spacing: 0.14em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		color: var(--terracotta);
	}

	h1,
	h2 {
		margin: 0;
		line-height: 1.05;
	}

	h1 {
		font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 6vw, 4.8rem);
		letter-spacing: -0.05em;
	}

	h2 {
		font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 3vw, 2rem);
		margin-bottom: 14px;
	}

	.lede {
		max-width: 42rem;
		font-size: 1.08rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
		color: var(--slate);
	}

	.links {
		display: flex;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		gap: 12px;
		margin-top: 20px;
	}

	a {
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		padding: 12px 16px;
		border-radius: 999px;
		border: 1px solid rgba(201, 106, 58, 0.28);
		background: rgba(201, 106, 58, 0.08);
		color: var(--ink);
		text-decoration: none;
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	ul,
	ol {
		margin: 0;
		padding-left: 20px;
		line-height: 1.8;
		color: var(--slate);
	}

	@media (max-width: 640px) {
		body {
			padding: 20px 14px 36px;
		}

		.hero,
		.panel {
			padding: 22px;
			border-radius: 20px;
		}
	}
</style>
